46 «Omai convien che tu così ti spoltre», 47 disse ’l maestro; «ché, seggendo in piuma, 48 in fama non si vien, né sotto coltre;
49 sanza la qual chi sua vita consuma, 50 cotal vestigio in terra di sé lascia, 51 qual fummo in aere e in acqua la schiuma.

query.result:
55 A longer staircase is necessary that one descends;
56 it is not enough to have departed from these.
57 If you understand me, now do so that it avails you.

64 Speaking he went so as not to appear weak;
65 whence a voice came from the other ditch,
66 to form words inconvenient.

67 I do not know what he said, although over the ridge
68 I was of the arch already that crosses here;
69 but he who spoke seemed moved to anger.

70 I was turned downwards, but the living eyes
71 could not go to the bottom because of the darkness;
72 for which I said: “Master, make that you arrive

73 from the other side and let us dismount the wall;
74 because, as I hear from here and do not understand,
75 thus downwards I see and figure nothing.”

