Please translate each line literally into English.

143 Pistoia in pria d’i Neri si dimagra;
144 poi Fiorenza rinova gente e modi.

145 Tragge Marte vapor di Val di Magra
146 ch’è di torbidi nuvoli involuto;
147 e con tempesta impetüosa e agra

148 sovra Campo Picen fia combattuto;
149 ond’ ei repente spezzerà la nebbia,
150 sì ch’ogne Bianco ne sarà feruto.

query.result:
143 Pistoia first of the Blacks will grow thin;
144 then Florence will renew people and customs.

145 Mars draws vapor from the Val di Magra
146 which is enveloped in murky clouds;
147 and with impetuous and harsh tempest

148 over Campo Picen will be fought;
149 whence he will suddenly break the fog,
150 so that every White will be wounded in it.
